<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٧٨٩ - قَالَ مَعْمَرٍ ,<span class="c5"> وَقَالَ قَتَادَةُ:</span> <span class="c3">{ثُمَّ لَمْ تَكُنْ فِتْنَتُهُمْ}</span> <span class="c4">[الأنعام: ٢٣]</span> ,<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«مَقَالَتُهُمْ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٧٩٠ -<span class="c5"> قَالَ مَعْمَرٌ:</span> <span class="c1">" سَمِعْتُ مَنَ ,<span class="c5"> يَقُولُ:</span> مَعْذِرَتُهُمْ "</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>